channel.title: Help! Model Making Error
channel.description:
So I just finished making my custom sword from scratch, but when I tried to open it in datmaker (its .mqo extension) to convert it to a .dat it said MQO invalid file format.
Someone said something about lines, idk, help?
Of course it could be because my sword has 13963 faces... Anyway to decrease?
